'''Khalid Al-Ghannam''' ({{langx|ar|خالد الغنام}}; born 8 November 2000) is a Saudi Arabian professional [[association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[Midfielder#Winger|winger]] for [[Saudi Pro League]] side [[Al-Ettifaq FC|Al-Ettifaq]] and the [[Saudi Arabia national football team|Saudi Arabia national team]].<ref>{{cite web |title=خالد عيسى الغنام - Khalid Al Ghannam |url=https://www.kooora.com/?player=126368}}</ref>

==Career==
Al-Ghannam started his career at the youth teams of [[Al-Qadsiah FC|Al-Qadsiah]] at 13 in 2013. On 22 January 2019, Al-Ghannam signed his first professional contract with the club.<ref>{{cite web |title=خالد الغنام قدساوياً حتى 2022 |url=https://twitter.com/qadisiyah1967/status/1087746767255416833}}</ref> On 19 April 2019, he made his first-team debut in a 2–0 loss against [[Al-Batin FC|Al-Batin]].<ref>{{cite web |title=الباطن يعزز حظوظه بالبقاء.. ويكسب القادسية بثنائية |url=https://sabq.org/v2Kt5T}}</ref> On 19 August 2019, Al-Ghannam signed a contract extension with Al-Qadsiah, keeping him at the club until 2024.<ref>{{cite web |title=ادارة النادي تمدد عقد اللاعب خالد الغنام لـ 5 سنوات قادمه وذلك حتى 2024م|url=https://twitter.com/qadisiyah1967/status/1160606682747166720}}</ref> On 29 January 2020, Al-Ghannam left his boyhood club and signed a 5-year contract with [[Saudi Professional League|Pro League]] champions [[Al-Nassr FC|Al-Nassr]].<ref>{{cite web |title=النصر يشتري عقد خالد الغنام من القادسية |url=https://spl.com.sa/ar/node/3185 |access-date=30 January 2020 |archive-date=16 August 2023 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20230816160958/https://spl.com.sa/ar/node/3185 |url-status=dead }}</ref> The reported fee was [[Saudi riyal|SAR]]20 million, in addition to [[Faraj Al-Ghushayan]] joining Al-Qadsiah on loan.<ref>{{cite web |title=20 مليونا تنقل الغنام إلى النصر |url=https://arriyadiyah.com/676599}}</ref> He made 16 appearances for Al-Qadsiah in all competitions and scored once against [[Al-Bukayriyah FC|Al-Bukayriyah]].

On 28 January 2023, Al-Ghannam joined [[Al-Fateh SC|Al-Fateh]] on a six-month loan.<ref>{{cite web |title=الفتح يستعير الغنام من النصر |url=https://arriyadiyah.com/795008}}</ref>

On 30 January 2024, Al-Ghannam joined [[Al-Ettifaq FC|Al-Ettifaq]] on a four-and-a-half-year deal.<ref>{{cite web |title=لاعب النصر خالد الغنام يدعم هجوم الاتفاق حتى 2028 |url=https://ettifaq.com/news/30-01-2024-2/}}</ref> On 2 September 2024, Al-Ghannam joined [[Al Hilal SFC|Al-Hilal]] on a one-year loan.<ref>{{cite web |title=رسميا.. الهلال يضم خالد الغنام|url=https://www.kooora.com/?n=1352217}}</ref>

